  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a large cast-iron pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute.",
    "Add the lemon zest, lime zest, and orange zest and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the Gruyère cheese and cook until melted and smooth.",
    "Stir in the almonds and parsley.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Deglaze the pan with a dash of lemon juice to loosen any browned bits.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and serve warm."
